org.batfish.common

Class Version

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.common.Version

  • public final class Version
extends Object
    A utility class to determine the version of Batfish being used and check compatibility between different endpoints across API calls.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static String INCOMPATIBLE_VERSION
      A special version string that is incompatible with all other version.

    • Method Summary

      static String getCompleteVersionString()
      Returns string indicating the current build of Batfish and Z3.
      static String getVersion()
      Returns the version of the current build of Batfish, or UNKNOWN_VERSION if the version could not be detected.
      static String getZ3Version()
      Returns the version of the current build of Z3, or UNKNOWN_VERSION if the version could not be detected.

      • isCompatibleVersion

        public static boolean isCompatibleVersion(String myName,
                                          String otherName,
                                          @Nullable
                                          String otherVersion)
        Returns true if the given version of some other endpoint is compatible with the Batfish version of this process.

        At the time of writing, compatibility is determined on having identical major and minor versions.
